Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten one crucial thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not protecting everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is I... who am always... being protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust... Bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their true strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not "One", but "Many"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A side effect of the Lost Magic, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I overused it considerably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's magic power \Nwill be returned to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a man by the name of Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:52.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost his mind after supposedly \Nbeing possessed by the ghost of Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tragic man who traverses \Na life of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was someone you held dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that was all the work of Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was an 8-year plan to have the Magic \NCouncil turn a blind eye to our actions at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a fearsome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades trusts her more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so fixated \Non searching for Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic at the beginning of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To get closer to the One Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what happens when you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:05.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal dreamt of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power is welling up within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is filling with magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our power is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it seems like our \Nmagic power is back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Carla and the others are late \Ngetting here because of what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Azuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their magic power is back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With even Gildarts here \Nlosing his magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even a match for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your power back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a proctor of this exam, it ain't \Ndignified for me to take a beating like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta put on a good show \Nin front of those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a fight where \Nwe can fly even higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we fight seriously now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An infinite gravity well \Nthat sucks in everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Dimguil's Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:56.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast these foolish Fairies with all \Nthat sadness, and return them to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we are caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my Figure Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't work on someone with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a man I can count \Non with his eyes wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be controlling you for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Countin' on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spell is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fly so bad, how \Nabout I send you flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke my spell to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for what's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Écriture of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your magic \Npower is back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's... will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to believe me or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Zeref and leaving this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... defeat Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Ul's spell, Iced Shell, you \Nshould be able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can carry \Nout what Ul and I have wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that weakness from \Nbefore was just some bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 'cause things are a little easier, \Nit's not like we're fully recovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, don't you think \Nyou're going a little fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta! I have to think of Gramps here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't know what's happened to everyone \Nelse unless we get back to the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry I can't walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:56.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, li'l kitty. You {\i1}do{\i0} understand the \Nsituation we're in when you said that, {\i1}right{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they say, care killed the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I am hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I ate was the \Nfire from that God Slayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I beat the crap out of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, me too. Cana's heavier \Nthan you'd think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana's unconscious, but that's \Nstill a terrible thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's not always me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was curious, so I climbed way up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant tree growing on the island \Nhas collapsed down to the roots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:40.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means the felling of the tree was \Nthe cause of our magic power drying up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is called the Tenrou Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it gives divine protection \Nto those in the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno the details, but anyone who's got \Na Fairy Tail mark can't die or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:56.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's why all the \Ninjured people made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:13:00.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, why did our magic power return?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tree is still toppled...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot relax yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we must stay on our guard \Nwhile our magic power recovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:25.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... will defeat Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell requires the caster \Nto give up their life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know full well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't for you, or for Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Gajeel and Mira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use healing magic right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the offer, \Nbut look at how many...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And look here... You've \Nbeen using magic all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to rest a little, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy attacked us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:15:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, for some unknown reason, \Nour magic power suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a close call, but Fried \Nand Bickslow fought for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even before that, everyone had \Nalready been injured here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten so dire without \Nme even realizing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cheerful characters like us can't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So even the Master and Cana are casualties...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grimoire Heart battleship \Nis anchored off to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering we need to defend this camp, \Nhow about splitting into two teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One attack team, and one defense team?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul... Ultear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving this island like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, I haven't found Gray yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Zeref have to do with Ul's wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was killed by Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get revenge, Ul chased \Nafter Grimoire Heart behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After Ul's death, I found her \Ndiary and learned the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get revenge, I \Ninfiltrated Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Hades's magic power was \Nbeyond anything I could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:22.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul knew this, which is why \Nshe mastered Iced Shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to master it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Ul's blood \Nruns through my veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only magic I know of right now \Nthat can defeat Hades is Iced Shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will seal him away, outside this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so that no one will ever find him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not handing him over to Hades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you're the only one who can \Ncarry out what Ul and I have wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He actually bought that story \NI came up with on the spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes well, then Hades \Nand Gray will off each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't think of anything better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Master Hades?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref will be ours alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to trick Master Hades?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Hades... Everyone should just \Ndance in the palm of my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not handing Zeref over to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine, all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't put so \Nmuch confidence in Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:16.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he should at least \Nserve to distract Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the island before he catches on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Gray are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill her, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she can't fight any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Gray have \Neven a hint of a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be destroyed by Hades, \Nor die from Iced Shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even if you manage to survive, \Nyou'll have lost your precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you catch on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never believed a damn thing you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:45.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you pretended to believe me in \Norder to find out my true aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You naughty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided never to use that magic again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped you before 'cause \NI didn't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what Ul wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to continue living, \Nalong with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... I guess you're not \Nsuch a good boy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had hoped you'd get lucky \Nand get rid of Hades for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I really didn't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're one of that \Nwoman's beloved pupils...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've chosen the most painful \Nway to die, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, rotten daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you a lesson \Nin your mother's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made one big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the 7 Kin of Purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:06.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stand a chance against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've beaten all the \Nenemies around for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to take on the bossman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:05.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to kill your buzz, but you \Nhardly show up next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character doesn't \Nshow up? I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.78,0:24:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're only just \Nbarely the main character, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, I'm the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.94,0:24:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Divine Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealousy doesn't become you, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, I didn't see a \Nshot with you in the preview...
